50|$|<b>Alitretinoin,</b> or 9-cis-retinoic acid, {{is a form}} {{of vitamin}} A. It is also used in {{medicine}} as an antineoplastic (anti-cancer) agent developed by Ligand Pharmaceuticals. It is a first generation retinoid. Ligand gained Food and Drug Administration (FDA) approval for <b>alitretinoin</b> in February 1999.|$|E
